import React from 'react'
import { Title, Subtitle, Centered } from './styles'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import UserName from './username'
import FormInput from '../TodoList/components/FormInput'
import { useState } from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Home = () => {
  const [userName, setUserName] = useState("")
  return(
    <>
      <Subtitle>
        Please enter your name below
      </Subtitle>
      <Centered>
        <FormInput
          type="text"
          placeholder="Type item here"
          value={userName}
          setValue={setUserName}
        />  
      </Centered>
      <Title primary>
        Hello {userName} and welcome to CL2C@hsa! 
      </Title>
      <Title>
        Or in other words Coding Level II @ HSA 
      </Title>
      <Link to="/list" style={{color: "Yellow"}}>Go to Todo List</Link>      
    </>
  )
}


export default Home
